{"tid":928981,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《是咁的》合作過　林秀怡撐黃子恆係好人","createTime":"2018-12-05T09:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T10:56:06.000Z","uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22a5be966591ba58e4ec5000a5a95aa7f97ecf04","tid":928981,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"藝人林秀怡與黃子恆於劇集《是咁的，法官閣下》中有多場合作戲份。秀怡接受東網訪問，對於黃子恆食國產粉絲一事，問到會否覺得子恆是花弗男及會否對此事覺得驚訝？她謂：「平時佢係一個好好的前輩，但其他嘢就等佢自己回應啦！我覺得佢係好人嚟！」 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181205/photo/bkn-20181205164748726-1205_00862_001_01p.jpg?20181205165511\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181205164748726-1205_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20181205165511&h=a55e7f6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4f3e197cbcbeaaa50d54fe91bde463d1f637c5a","tid":928981,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"條女<br />\nwho?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bebcf58de653a95521dd94ef9e8b949e7f1089","tid":928981,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"林秀怡同黃子恆扑野個時有冇戴套？"},{"pid":"4aa1861f3bcefe03bf9db638957a46c72dea4ae6","tid":928981,"uid":32114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"31bebcf58de653a95521dd94ef9e8b949e7f1089","tid":928981,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"林秀怡同黃子恆扑野個時有冇戴套？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"林秀怡: 臨出時佢有掹出去，佢係好人黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafeb881f9aa66d8e803bb2440bd6a17cd6d0216","tid":928981,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im